                <note rend="inline" type="source">125.953/11–749: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Tsingtao</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hawthorne</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tsingtao</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-11-07">November 7,
                            1949.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received November 7—3:12 a. m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>605. ReDeptel 333, November 4.<note n="21" xml:id="d1459fn21">Not printed.</note>
                    Consulate General officially closed and final accounts submitted as of October
                    15. Funds may be remitted through New York office Hong Kong and Shanghai Banking
                    Corporation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hawthorne</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
